• About me •

Driven teamplayer with great interest in IT and new technology. Long experience from financial management and good at structuring and streamlining my work. Has experience from purchasing and project work and customer, supplier and authority contact. I think that problem solving, troubleshooting and automation in data, IT and network is among the most fun there is to do.

• Främsta kompetenser •

• Problemlösning • Active Directory • Microsoft Azure • Amazon AWS • Molnlösningar • Felsöknig • Konfigurering • Budget • Kostnadskontroll • Kundsupport • Hyper-v • Administration (system, server etc)

• Work experience •

Codic Education

• Cloud Developer Internship •

Jan 2022 – current • Remote

Tidnings AB Metro

• Distribution manager Sweden •

Jun 2018 - Nov 2019 • Remote

Responsibility for all purchases regarding printing, paper, distribution for Metro's three newspaper editions and other printing products such as Metro Mode, appendices etc. Personnel responsibility for two people in two different offices in Sweden. Total responsibility for negotiations and contract signing for the department. Lead and develop the distribution department's personnel, projects, budget and follow-up of these, as well as responsibility for day-to-day operations with prioritization and resource allocation of staff and partners. Responsible for analysis and development of our key figures such as scope, circulation, economy. Lead the development of our distribution system and mobile solutions by digitizing large parts of Metro's distribution. Project management for various projects within the department's responsibilities such as new newspaper format, new revenue and products

• Distributionscontroller with purchasing responsibilities •

Aug 2009 - May 2018 • Gothenburg & Malmö

Analyze, monitor results and monitor profitability of the distribution department. Budget responsibility and budget follow-up, reports and forecasts for, among other things, paper, print & distribution for Metro's morning newspaper magazines and other newspaper products. Development of our key figures such as scope, circulation, economy. Create and develop PowerPoint presentations to the management team, salespeople and customers. Write, update and be responsible for agreements and daily checks that these were followed. Invoice management and accounting for all the department's invoices. Participate in negotiations with suppliers and partners. System responsibility for Metro's distribution system from 2010 to 2011.

• Distribution Manager Metro Riks & Metro Teknik •

Mar 2008 - Jul 2009 • Gothenburg

Responsible for the daily maintenance of Metro Riks & Metro Teknik. Assignments such as planning editions, reviewing possible returns, evaluating distribution points, daily contact with printing, haulage and other partners.

Metro Nordic

• Sales Support •

2007 - Mar 2008 • Gothenburg

Advertising booking, sales support, production of sales material, sales reporting, contact with advertisers and media agencies, daily control of advertisements in the newspaper.

OnOff Sverige

• Retail Sales •

2006 - 2007 • Gothenburg

Electronics sales, exposure, product replenishment, customer contact, checkout service.

Aller Media

• Advertisements Receiver •

2000 - 2006 • Helsingborg

Customer contact, invoicing, ad production, customer support, booking of ads, planning and placement of ads, Pdf production, web production of image and text. Worked in programs like, photoshop, illustrator, quarkXpress, Acrobat professional, freehand, toast, Mac os 9 and os X.

• Desktop Publishing Specialist •

1998 • Helsingborg

Scanning, mounting, uncovering, customer contact, proof printing. Worked in programs such as filemaker, photoshop, illustrator, indesign, PageMaker, Acrobat professional, Acrobat pdf server, Mac os 9 and os X and Windows NT.

• Education •

Campus Mölndal

• Cloud- and Virtualizationspecialst •

Nov 2020 – May 2022 • Remote

As a cloud and virtualization specialist, we learn to work with building cost-effective and smart IT environments so that companies have a functioning IT infrastructure. You are responsible for setting up the hardware, configuring servers and maintaining access, rights and administration of functions and roles.

Courses:

• Windows server, 30 YH-points • Active Directory, 30 YH-points • Servervirtualisering, 45 YH-points • Personal and professional development, 20 YH-points • Cloud platforms, 20 YH-points • IT Service Management and ITIL, 15 YH-points • Amazon AWS, 40 YH-points • Microsoft Azure, 40 YH-points • Internship, 90 YH-points • Master thesis, 20 YH-points.
